      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional driver at an accessible price point. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, but buyers should anticipate some upcoming maintenance items like brake pad replacement and a suspension refresh to restore its original ride quality. It\u2019s a dependable car that has served its previous owner well but is no longer in showroom condition.",
